      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older driver/project car being sold in poor overall condition. It shows heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, and buyers should expect noticeable age, use, and deferred maintenance. This is not a clean, turnkey example \u2014 it will need repairs, sorting, and general attention before anyone should expect it to be truly dependable. Best suited for someone looking for a budget project, parts car, or inexpensive driver to improve over time.",
