    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Fair-condition driver that shows normal age and use throughout. The exterior and interior both have visible wear, blemishes, and general signs of use, but it remains a presentable car you can enjoy as-is while improving over time. Expect some deferred maintenance and minor issues consistent with a used vehicle in this condition, so it\u2019s best suited for someone looking for an honest, affordable example rather than a perfect one.",
