    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Budget-priced car being sold in poor condition and best suited for a handy buyer, project, or parts use. It shows heavy wear and needs significant work, but if you\u2019re looking for an inexpensive starting point and know what you\u2019re getting into, it could still be worth a look. Honest car at an honest price.",
