    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers affordable transportation and strong value for the money. Best suited for buyers seeking a practical option they can put to work right away, with an honest presentation and a price that makes ownership accessible. If you're looking for low-cost entry into dependable daily driving, this is a compelling opportunity.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "If you\u2019re after an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person, this one is worth a look. It\u2019s not a showroom queen, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option that could make a great runaround, starter car, or little project for someone handy. Priced to reflect its condition, and offered by someone who believes in being easy to deal with and upfront. Come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-minded driver/project with a strong mechanical foundation and plenty of usable life left. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, shifts as it should, and the chassis feels composed for an older used car. Cosmetically it shows its age and will need attention in spots, but it remains a practical, approachable option for someone who wants dependable transportation, a weekend fixer, or an affordable platform to improve over time. If you know how to spot value in a rough-around-the-edges car, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true underdog with unmistakable presence, this car has the kind of worn-in charm that turns an ordinary drive into a story. It\u2019s the sort of vehicle for someone who sees opportunity where others see age\u2014a trusty companion for weekend projects, backroad errands, or a budget-friendly set of wheels with personality to spare. If you want something with character, curb appeal, and plenty of room to make it your own, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
