      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking low-cost transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and wear, but it offers an accessible entry point with honest value for the price. A smart option for someone who wants affordability first and room to make it their own.",
      "price": 5950.0,
